summary.purpose: Re-exports all types, interfaces, and enums from the library's three sub-modules as a single public entry point.
summary.problem_solved: Enables consumers to import any symbol from akeyless-types-commons through a single package path without knowing internal folder structure.

internal.why_used: Re-exports all type definitions (Geo, TObject, NumberObject, socket types)
Re-exports all interface definitions (Car, Client, Site, Board, Equipment, User, etc.)
Re-exports all enumeration definitions (feature flags, board/equipment/unit status, etc.)

exports.name: types (re-export)
exports.description_one_line: Re-exports everything from the types sub-module

exports.name: interfaces (re-export)
exports.description_one_line: Re-exports everything from the interfaces sub-module

exports.name: enums (re-export)
exports.description_one_line: Re-exports everything from the enums sub-module

symbols.name: types (re-export)
symbols.description_one_line: Barrel re-export of all type definitions from the types sub-module

details.what_it_does: Publishes all exports from './types' (index.ts → global.ts, socket.ts) under the package root. Consumers receive Geo, TObject, NumberObject, SOCKET_EVENTS, SocketEventMap, RedisUpdateType, RedisUpdatePayload, SocketCallbackResponse, and CollectionConfig.

minimal_correct.title: Import a type from the root entry point

symbols.name: interfaces (re-export)
symbols.description_one_line: Barrel re-export of all interface definitions from the interfaces sub-module

details.what_it_does: Publishes all exports from './interfaces' (index.ts → global.ts, credits.ts, go.ts) under the package root. Consumers receive TimestampType, firebase_timestamp, Site, NxUser, MobileAppUser, GoUser, Client, Board, Peripheral, Car, UnitExtra, UsersUnits, LastLocationCar, CarState, CanbusParameter, Equipment, EquipmentOption, EventFromDevice, EventFromDevice_Ruptela, EventFromDevice_Erm, ErmStates, ReportMeta, ReportMetaHeader, ReportMetaDataType, ReportParameterDataType, ReportDataRow, GprsItem, CreditType, CreditItem, CreditAuditAction, CreditAuditItem, GoMobileUserRole, GoAuthModel, GoUserRole, GoCarLink, RoleInToken, and GoUserCar.

minimal_correct.title: Import domain interfaces from the root entry point

symbols.name: enums (re-export)
symbols.description_one_line: Barrel re-export of all enum definitions from the enums sub-module

details.what_it_does: Publishes all exports from './enums' (index.ts → global.ts, car_events.ts, features.ts) under the package root. Consumers receive DefaultClient, BoardStatus, EquipmentStatus, EquipmentStatusReason, UnitStatus, ClientStatus, LanguageOptions, CountryOptions, SiteType, RuptelaEventEnum, FeaturesBoard, FeaturesClient, FeaturesDashboard, FeaturesInstaller, FeaturesToolbox, UserPermissionsObject, and userPermissionsObjectValue.

minimal_correct.title: Import enums from the root entry point
